{"id":232818706,"title":"#分享【雙螺旋 Helix】","content":"http://i.imgur.com/FAj5LGP.jpg\n2014年的作品看名字就知是部生物相關的影集，我也是因為這部才記熟這個單字，DNA雙股螺旋的Helix，故事講述疾病控制中心的專家Alan Farragut博士和Julia Walker博士前往北極圈附近調查一次神秘的病毒爆發，免不了要避免人類的滅絕，喜歡這種病毒、生化危機類型的應該會喜歡上這部，第一季營造的非常驚悚刺激，時不時會被感染者嚇到，而人物私下的暗潮洶湧也是一大看點，在北極的設計也是滿特別的，場景設計也是不馬虎。\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/3Kttvkb.jpg\n\n第二季就有點複雜，故事時間軸推進了不少加上來回時間線的跳動真的滿燒腦的，不像是第一季比較直觀，但是有Sarah(Jordan Hayes 飾)非常的賞心悅目，加上主角也叫Alan真的是必須看下去，整體伏筆鋪陳的不錯，故事也是滿新奇有趣的，病毒爆發跟永生的議題，喜歡殭屍片的朋友可以考慮，前兩季故事都滿完整的，最後結尾更是神展開，可惜沒有要續訂了，可惜成為被腰斬的作品！\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/Elq8Qlr.jpg\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/BgWCntw.jpg\n\n#2014 #雙螺旋 #Helix #Syfy \n--\n自己創立的影集分享帳號，歡迎追蹤交流\nhttps://www.instagram.com/allen.attic/","excerpt":"2014年的作品看名字就知是部生物相關的影集，我也是因為這部才記熟這個單字，DNA雙股螺旋的Helix，故事講述疾病控制中心的專家Alan Farragut博士和Julia Walker博士前往北極圈","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"28e79ba0-8ded-4acc-a6b2-f015bdef7605","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-03T12:53:25.083Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-03T12:53:25.083Z","commentCount":4,"likeCount":13,"tags":[],"topics":["歐美影集板","美劇","觀後感"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"歐美影集","forumAlias":"ea_series","school":"欸冷影劇閣樓","department":"allen.attic","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":12},{"id":"4b018f48-e184-445f-adf1-fc8e04ba09b9","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/FAj5LGP.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/3Kttvkb.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/Elq8Qlr.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/BgWCntw.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"df709e6d-03ce-4c4b-9620-4cae4d24a91d","url":"https://i.imgur.com/FAj5LGPl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/FAj5LGPl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/FAj5LGPl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail